"36:39:3" : {s: 36, a: 39, w: 3, r: "نزل", t: "مَنَازِلَ", l: "مَنَازِل", lc: 2, tl: "manāzila", lb: "মনজিল, বাড়ি, ঘর, বিশ্রামস্থল",e: "phases", b: "কতগুলো পরিমাপ-স্তরে", f: 2, rm: "to descend, come down, go down, happen, alight at, settle in a place, lodge. anzala - to send down, give. nazulun - that which is prepared for a guests entertainment, abode, gift. manzil - mansion, station. nazzala - to cause to descend, send down. tanziil - sending down, divine revelation, orderly arrangement and authentic compilation, gradual revelation."},
